itunes:subtitle: Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by Burt Kuntz from TV to discuss the guys’ favorite shows like “Seinfeld” and “It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia”, Burt tells all about why Joe Biden is a terrible candidate, Burt begrudgingly downloaded Tik Tok...
itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by Burt Kuntz from TV to discuss the guys’ favorite shows like “Seinfeld” and “It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia”, Burt tells all about why Joe Biden is a terrible candidate, Burt begrudgingly downloaded Tik Tok and ended up liking it, he announces his new upcoming podcast in conjunction with Drinkin’ Bros, and ends the show with telling us about his new movie with Chris Pine “Violence of Action.”
